snippet.textDisplay: Ok listen if you want to try a pizza like you never had before, make your way to Savo’s pizza in Pittston PA. It’s a square pizza, the call slices “Cuts” The pizza is light airy crust, creamy blend of cheeses and a sweet tasting sauce. I had a friend telling me about this place and how good it was and was like no pizza you ever had. I was like yea, yea, I’ve had many pizzas across NJ and NY and was like yea right. Well I finally had it. Now I drive 2hrs from NJ to go back there. Unbelievable you gotta try this. Once you start eating it you can’t put it down!! By far my favorite place ever!!!
